sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuthSrv as OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Backend as Dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Operator as KServe/Notebooks Operator

    Note over User,OAuthSrv: Flow 1: User Login and Dashboard Access
    User->>Route: GET / (HTTPS/443)
    Route->>OAuth: Forward (HTTPS/8443)<br/>TLS 1.2+ service cert
    OAuth->>OAuthSrv: OAuth authentication flow<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    OAuthSrv-->>OAuth: OAuth token
    OAuth-->>User: Set OAuth cookie<br/>Redirect to dashboard
    User->>Route: GET / with OAuth cookie
    Route->>OAuth: Forward with cookie
    OAuth->>Backend: Proxy to backend<br/>HTTP/8080 with Bearer token
    Backend-->>OAuth: Static assets (HTML/JS/CSS)
    OAuth-->>Route: Forward response
    Route-->>User: Dashboard UI (HTTPS/443)

    Note over User,Operator: Flow 2: API Request - Create Notebook
    User->>Route: POST /api/notebooks<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token cookie
    Route->>OAuth: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    OAuth->>Backend: Proxy request<br/>HTTP/8080, Bearer token header
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Create Notebook CR<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Notebook CR created
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event (Notebook CR)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Notebook Pod
    Backend-->>OAuth: JSON response<br/>HTTP/8080
    OAuth-->>Route: Forward response<br/>HTTPS/8443
    Route-->>User: Success response<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 3: Metrics Collection
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus
    Prometheus->>Route: GET /metrics<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    Route->>OAuth: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    Note over OAuth: skip-auth-regex=^/metrics
    OAuth->>Backend: Proxy (HTTP/8080)<br/>Auth skipped
    Backend-->>OAuth: Prometheus metrics
    OAuth-->>Route: Forward metrics
    Route-->>Prometheus: Metrics data

    Note over Backend,K8sAPI: Flow 4: Dashboard Configuration Query
    User->>Route: GET /api/config<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    Route->>OAuth: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    OAuth->>Backend: Proxy (HTTP/8080)<br/>Bearer token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: GET OdhDashboardConfig CR<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: OdhDashboardConfig data
    Backend-->>OAuth: JSON config<br/>HTTP/8080
    OAuth-->>Route: Forward response
    Route-->>User: Configuration data
